\subsection{Physical implementations}

During the \ac{DB} phase, we measure the round-trip time of electromagnetic 
waves.
This means that we must add as little overhead from processing as possible 
during this step.
This means that we need dedicated hardware.

\Textcite{DBonSmartphones} evaluated how well one could do to implement \ac{DB} 
protocols on smartphones without hardware support.
